as the number of neighbor oxygens within a distance ഛ0.32 nm ͑the ﬁrst minimum of the radial distribution function at ␳ = 0.984 g / cm3 and T = 284 K ͓109͔͒ from a central O atom. q͑z͒ is deﬁned as ͓107͔

