͓86͔ In this work the values of P do not include corrections due to

the cutoff ͑rc = 0.79 nm͒ used when calculating the plate-water, plate-plate, and water-water Lennard-Jones interactions. For

the case of a Lennard-Jones ͑LJ͒ liquid, the correction to P is

given by ͓M. P. Allen and D. J. Tildesley, Computer Simula-

tion of Liquids ͑Oxford University Press, Oxford, 2004͔͒

⌬P

=

